column2: ... look, these are the projections for the next couple of years.
[shake,7]Wow[!shake]. The replacement rate is [wave]really[!wave] low there.
Yeah! Who knows what's going to happen.
[wave]Impostor![!wave] Why do you have my face?
Yeah wait why do you look [shake,7]just like us[!shake]
We're eating your food. It's going to expire.
We're from [wave]the future[!wave]. Keira, where do you wanna eat?
No, [wave]we're making plans[!wave]. If we talk to you too much, spoilers!
But now we know that we live long enough to come back to eat the food.
Expired food is expired food. She won't mind.
You [wave]technically[!wave] will. All right, anywhere you want to go before we head out?
Dunno, like a couple years older than us. I have the shirt that... I was wearing?
